&lt;li&gt;&lt;br&gt;
If using an EQ, try turning it off to see if it fixes the problem. &lt;br&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;br&gt;
If not using an EQ, try turning it on and boosting the bass a little bit.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;br&gt;
To determine if the problem is in the source device, try connecting the speaker to a different device (phone/tablet/music player/etc.).&lt;br&gt;
